No. 732,

Misc.

Rich v. United States. Solicitor General Griswold, Assistant Attorney General Vinson, Jerome M. Feit, and Marshall T. Golding for the United States.

C. A. 4th Cir. Certiorari denied.

The Chief Justice is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted. Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
